OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMostly dry with sunny spells
OL,6,Ffor many at first. However, showers
OL,7,Fare expected to develop across the
OL,8,Fsouthwest, although these will be
OL,9,Flighter and less frequent than on
OL,10,FThursday. Scattered showers will also
OL,11,Fcontinue across Scotland and Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FClear spells at first,
OL,15,Fturning wet and windy from the
OL,16,Fsouthwest overnight, with rain
OL,17,Freaching all but Scotland by dawn.
OL,18,FWinds strengthening, becoming gusty
OL,19,Fwith coastal gales in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
