OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy for most with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, locally heavy at
OL,7,Ffirst. Becoming brighter from the west
OL,8,Fwith showers in the south. Windy, with
OL,9,Fcoastal gales in the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
